# Ignore everything by default; this repository intentionally tracks only
# extraction inputs, config, docs, and pinned mod references.
*
!*/

!.gitignore
!.gitmodules
!LICENSE
!README.md

!.github/
!.github/**

!manifest.json
!tools/
!tools/*.py

!data/
!data/**
!*.cnut

!docs/
!docs/**

!mods/
!mods/README.md
!mods/reforged
.DS_Store
